Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.93,Arial,Susu Alessandra,0,0,0,,Ku pingin yang lebih sederhana seperti "cium aku Darling".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:07.46,Arial,Susu Alessandra,0,0,0,,Haaa!!! Darling cepatlah pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.60,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Kajika, lihatlah kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.60,Arial,Kajika Harumi,0,0,0,,Kakak ini memalukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.40,Arial,Susu Alessandra,0,0,0,,Sawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.70,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Sus.
