Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.60,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Aku senang jika difotokan, tapi aku perlu melakukan rekaman terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:37.83,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Dengan itu, dia adalah Sawara Harumi. Perempuan tertua di 777 dan senang untuk hidup bebas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:41.50,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Walau dia sering mendapati masalah, tapi dia dapat dihandalkan juga loh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.50,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Aku bahagia sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.33,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Biarkan kufoto dirimu lebih banyak lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.30,Arial,Kajika Harumi,0,0,0,,Kakak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.86,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Duh... Uwaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.56,Arial,Kajika Harumi,0,0,0,,Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.96,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Ha... Ahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.23,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, dia sering mendapati masalah juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.80,Arial,Shinju Harumi,0,0,0,,Ya ampun, sedang apa kalian semua?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.50,Arial,Susu Alessandra,0,0,0,,Ah, Shinju!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.26,Arial,Shinju Harumi,0,0,0,,Sedang apa? Rekaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:09.66,Arial,Susu Alessandra,0,0,0,,Coney meminta kita untuk membuat video perkenalan kita semua di 777.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.36,Arial,Shinju Harumi,0,0,0,,Oh begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:15.63,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Huft, Para adik-adik tercintaku
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.66,Arial,Sawara Harumi,0,0,0,,Shinju dan Kajika
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:35.33,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Tiga bunga spesial dari distrik perbelanjaan kecil, inilah tiga saudari cantik dari pasar ikan Uoharu. Sekarang lihatlah kehebatan kita!
