Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:56.25,Arial,Cek lagi,0,0,0,,Beberapa waktu lalu, setiap hari ada penampilan disini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.52,Arial,,0,0,0,,Hee...
